<p>&quot;Seriously, dude,&quot; Beetle said as the friends entered Orion's house, &quot;it's been several sols and I haven't seen you and Zhet talk, like, at all.&quot;</p>
<p>&quot;I said I didn't want to talk about it,&quot; Rion said monotonously as he led them to his room.</p>
<p>&quot;Well clearly you need to,&quot; Stella said following behind. &quot;You've been moping for sols and you won't even tell us what happened.&quot; As they passed Lucifer's room, he popped out.</p>
